Who made this?

9
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,240
Why is the face covered with cloth?

10
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:28,120
It's said the ones seeing the evil god

11
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,960
will die within three days,

12
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:32,680
as miserably as Qian Hansheng died.

13
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,360
So Mr. Qian

14
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,720
saw the evil god statue

15
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:36,680
and then died?

16
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:41,000
Can you please stop echoing each other?

17
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,600
About what's underneath,

18
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,160
can't we go down and look?

19
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,360
Detective He,

20
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,320
you're a police officer, you go.

21
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,160
Bao Long.

22
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,080
Boss.

23
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,120
What did you say you found just now?

24
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:55,360
Boss, after thorough search,

25
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:58,760
I noticed just one carpet
in the living room.

26
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,320
Any clues?

27
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,960
Nothing much, just the usual.

28
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,880
I don't believe monsters and demons.

29
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,600
Let's go have a look at Mr. Qian's body.

30
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,400
