I'll find it for you.

129
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:44,040
For every customer,

130
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,560
I keep a photo.

131
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,760
For advertising.

132
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:53,760
Oh, there was another strange thing.

133
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,920
